1286
01:21:23,440 --> 01:21:28,720
I just swapped the 1 over
length of output number I.

1287
01:21:28,720 --> 01:21:30,880
Just swapped it here.

1288
01:21:30,880 --> 01:21:33,360
I'm going to explain
