1291
01:21:45,920 --> 01:21:49,440
So if you're in a
very long output,

1292
01:21:49,440 --> 01:21:51,680
this will be 1 over
a very long output.

1293
01:21:51,680 --> 01:21:54,720
It will be a small number.

1294
01:21:55,440 --> 01:21:57,440
If it's a short
output, it's going

1295
01:21:57,440 --> 01:21:59,120
to be 1 over a short number.

1296
01:21:59,120 --> 01:22:01,440
It's going to be a big number.

1297
01:22:04,240 --> 01:22:11,360
And the term on the right
