1330
01:24:31,440 --> 01:24:33,840
If the tokens in
a short output, it

1331
01:24:33,840 --> 01:24:38,640
will be down weighted even more
than if it's in a long output.

1332
01:24:38,640 --> 01:24:43,680
So in other words,
what you're going to do

1333
01:24:43,680 --> 01:24:47,920
is to prefer longer
bad outputs as opposed

1334
01:24:47,920 --> 01:24:51,360
